data.description: Discover this exceptional property featuring two homes on a spacious plot of land! The main residence, boasting 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, showcases contemporary updates in the lower level living spaces, including new plumbing and electrical systems, while the expansive upper floorplan awaits your personalization. This house also includes a studio space in the basement which you could use as another rental space or an extra living/office space., while the expansive upper floorplan awaits your personalization. This house also includes a studio space in the basement which you could use as another rental space or an extra living/office space.   Additionally, a well-maintained 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom second home is occupied by a tenant, providing reliable income. Including a laundry room, garage, and an open living space, this property offers practicality and potential for the current tenant or any future tenants. Use the rental income to finance renovations on the main house, unlocking its full value and creating equity. Perfect for the hands-on homeowner seeking a live-in project with immediate income opportunities!
